‼️GIVEAWAY ‼️
To all the mothers out there, Happy Mother’s Day to you! And if you happen to be too busy to buy your mom a treat, it’s not too late as I’ll be giving away 4 packets of @dansbitessg to 1 lucky winner so that you can share with mommy!
🔻
As you know in my earlier post(count 16 post earlier, ) @dansbitessg is Singapore’s 1st Brownie Crisp which Comes in 4 flavors
⭐️Dark Chocolate
⭐️Dark Chocolate w Mixed Nuts
⭐️Milk Tea
⭐️White Chocolate !
It’s taste is that of a Rich classic brownie yet infused with a creative crisp twist in it! Crunchy and yet still have the brownie experience once your bite through! It can be paired with milk, coffee/Tea or if you are like me, I prefer to eat it on its own!
🔻
Here’s how you can participate ! All you have to do is
✔️Like the Post
✔️Follow @makanwarrior and @dansbitessg
✔️Tag 1 friend (multiple entries are allowed) and mention which flavor you want to try!
📣Giveaway will be close on the 17 May 23:59 So good luck!
